job.title: Ministry of Defence Recruitment 2021 – Apply Offline for 42 Fireman Vacancies in New Delhi
job.body:
Total vacancies:42

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Fireman
  • Motor Driver
  • Vehicle Mechanic
  • Laborer
  • Carpenter

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for the 10th pass has been published by the Ministry of Defence for Fireman vacancies in New Delhi. If you are searching for a government job in New Delhi then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Fireman, from 22.05.2021, and till 11.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in New Delhi and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for Fireman vacancies in New Delhi, your 10th/12th must be completed by a recognized Board

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 22.05.2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is 11.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 18 to 25  years old. 

Ministry of Defence Fireman Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the New Delhi Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 19900 – 45700.

How to apply for Ministry of Defence Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Fireman. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  • First, go to the official website of the Ministry of Defence and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification.
  • Print out the application form
  • Fill up the details asked in the application form by blue or black pen
  • Now send this application form to the address mentioned below
  • ASC Battalion near Barfani Mandir Opposite SD College, Pathankot Cantt (Punjab)

Download Official notification pdf.
